ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisCERTAIN MARINE CARRIERS REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of fees for marine navigation services provided by the Canadian Coast Guard in the years 2008, 2009 and 2010 that were paid or payable by marine carriers operating in Canadian waters from ports located south of 60ºN to locations in latitudes north of 60ºN.
